WorkItem.Description:
I noticed when I went through the "Unknown" and "Other" items in my item cache that items purchasable with "Wintergrasp Marks of Honor" are set to be purchasable by [Unknown].
 
Example:
http://www.wowarmory.com/item-info.xml?i=44914
 
Ideally Rawr should recognize [Wintergrasp Mark of Honor] and additionally items purchased by them should be put in the "PvP" filter that comes with it.
